headline: QuantiPath Appoints Jeff Nauseda as Director of Market Development -- Bolstering Beef & Pet Food Reach Ahead of GenoPATHX Launch
summary: QuantiPath (quantipath.bio), the biotechnology company advancing genomic pathogen diagnostics for food safety, today announced the appointment of Jeff Nauseda as Director of Market Development, with principal responsibility for scaling QuantiPath's presence in the beef and pet food sectors. This strategic hire strengthens a leadership team that already offers deep coverage in poultry and swine.
